title: Appointments to SLFAC announced
content_text: The Government announced today (June 13) the re-appointment of three incumbent members to the Subventions and Lotteries Fund Advisory Committee (SLFAC) for a period of one year with effect from 1 June 2000. The three incumbent members are Mr Aaron Wan Chi-keung, Ms Wendy Wu Kit-ying and Mr Henry Lau King-chiu. They have been serving on the Committee for two years. Mr Aaron Wan chi-keung is actively
